{"tid":1903043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"進攻功能組別係要立會過半","createTime":"2020-02-28T17:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T03:21:00.000Z","uid":23194,"like":79,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"5d086ef547318e804e00fb2c0eb33f3e53d19c4e","tid":1903043,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"取消功能組別係香港人嘅共識<br />\n但係用乜嘢方法呢？<br />\n有人想佛系等美國用人權民主法案取消2020功能組別<br />\n但現實上，我唔認為美國會喺11月大選前會因為香港同中國攤牌<br />\n唔係話美國唔會幫香港，但係時機的確唔<br />\n加上執行上嗰班人從來冇諗過有乜嘢「實際」行動可以令美國咁做<br />\n<br />\n進攻功能組別的確冇可能因為咁樣而即時取消功能組別<br />\n我哋從來都知道呢條路唔係一步登天<br />\n立法會個半，短時間可以擋到23條立法國歌發信用評級系統<br />\n而我認為其中一樣重要功能就係可以否決財政預算<br />\n堵塞庫房外匯儲備送中<br />\n斷中共回血劍，配合美國<br />\n可以令佢哋係中美貿易戰乖乖挨打<br />\n引發支爆，失去中共唯一（經濟）管治的合法性<br />\n到該時候就是真正解放香港之時<br />\n<br />\n有人會質疑選舉過程政府可能會舞弊，例如掌心雷、換票箱、DQ等等，到時就真是人權民主法案發揮作用的時候。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人會問，當否決兩次財政預算，特首有權解散立法會。我認為這樣會跌入Dr. Strange 的無限循環<br />\n可能有人會認為中產公務員醫護受唔起政府財政停擺，但這樣冇辦法要光復香港就必須要受一些痛苦<br />\n學生可以為香港人擋子彈，成年人也要有經濟動盪的準備<br />\n<br />\n另一個問題係選舉入邊如何分配本土配額<br />\n我認為可以根據天琦一六年新東補選得票比例同泛民主派協調出選配額<br />\n希望係地區直選得到22至23席<br />\n所有代表民主陣營出選的候選人也必須提交投名狀<br />\n已表示他們會堅定反對23條國歌法信用評級系統等奧斯威爾式惡法，以及承諾不會出賣同路人<br />\n天琦講過：條條大佬通羅馬，放棄教條主義，邊個方法得就用邊個<br />\n<br />\n希望大家放下成見，唔好扼殺呢一個可能性，大家可以多加討論<br />\n最後一個問題就係，究竟熱普城屬唔屬於本土派？<br />\n認同就麻煩推一下，謝謝"},{"pid":"0500747f78c1c3405f0aabed05dc95fbc31c8562","tid":1903043,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:03:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a5dd73949144c2b181e017c88d13e6e1f4c66240","tid":1903043,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:06:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fb52d09d66978c8ae9a2cafb676f626bfb0654e","tid":1903043,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8bae741f366b3f625b061f11107f7389ac981e7","tid":1903043,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43f2679f437ea4ac288b6db9a2f7b26db9215f58","tid":1903043,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:11:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7054f9eb6add0f64828fc5a215dabb0a27e3fc95","tid":1903043,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32038e4903c8d82b1001556b0722646ae5964a89","tid":1903043,"uid":51761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:12:48.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9380ba24057d281eb78703bcc4fdddd3a6859982","tid":1903043,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"打咗好耐 推"},{"pid":"b4ab06a3ecc39a12a8f6beaa04f1f9cf99ba7b1e","tid":1903043,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:33:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c5f8ba8057809c01de345b512937557b4d483e6","tid":1903043,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"208c4f0cf4700ad97668f0f838dbe51e48808a9d","tid":1903043,"uid":14667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:40:49.000Z","msg":"推 重點無人睇"},{"pid":"b1f45616d86dcb87ed308a070663ba6785b219a1","tid":1903043,"uid":262464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:42:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9134c855c2de7ae2152fdf4d7318f1976eedfc0b","tid":1903043,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:44:30.000Z","msg":"要有真手足參選"},{"pid":"0b75833d75abaaeb71fd7dc7b5667d7bcae547e2","tid":1903043,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:55:02.000Z","msg":"仲可以用權力及特權法成立獨立調查委員會去清算違法警察，削弱警權，還政於民。<br />\n當然前提係有能力擋住警察衝擊立法會先。"},{"pid":"122e843f1dd7010c9e274f18353c0865b12dacf8","tid":1903043,"uid":39433,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後個問題已經話比人知你係泛民打手"},{"pid":"5b1646fe87b88133237996efa7105050b24f3c8f","tid":1903043,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T18:02:29.000Z","msg":"事實係必須搶攻功能組別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901931\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901931</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7d0bc4da3dac1ea8f187e209af7ceaf86aaa363e","tid":1903043,"uid":23194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"122e843f1dd7010c9e274f18353c0865b12dacf8","tid":1903043,"uid":39433,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T17:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後個問題已經話比人知你係泛民打手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T18:03:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔係本土派打手?"},{"pid":"b52d3fa075d7cabde515ccbbd77f5e23340b90f2","tid":1903043,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係連登講<br />\n自己入工會<br />\n落街幫手叫黃店參與<br />\n<br />\n功能組別最後一個月！決勝關鍵係工程、建築測量、飲食、批發零售、進出口！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901845</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［叫黃店登記］民間記者會：《一日一界別 &mdash; 飲食界》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901797</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d39f4d119659b1c0fa81dc9f0f45a9e7f488db20","tid":1903043,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T18:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48bb8fab34744a3e311dcc6d5786460502cc41d2","tid":1903043,"uid":186190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T18:22:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e19dfe174eb090fe851d8e741370a23aba1e3f04","tid":1903043,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T18:55:30.000Z","msg":"天琦四年前嘅票點同依家比呀"},{"pid":"571435c6293f297dc7ca3ceebf2802b38d0c24a0","tid":1903043,"uid":286309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:03:05.000Z","msg":"美國個牌並唔係佛系等嘅，的確如果美國9月前都係無出手嘅 ，就要硬食選舉靠自己。<br />\n<br />\n但係唔係佛系等嘅，仲有嘢做<br />\n5月會出份香港自治報告，如果香港人喺遊說方面做得好<br />\n將功能組別嘅存在＝沒有自治嘅關係寫入報告<br />\n<br />\n點實行要睇美國，不過我地可以加快呢個進程<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無人提過呢個方法<br />\n[反對與支持者請入] 進攻功能組别嘅Q&amp;A<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fdGvzS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fdGvzS</a>"},{"pid":"5ec78bf18e5a79b8a5b250a09650332a6fb1f171","tid":1903043,"uid":226155,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:06:12.000Z","msg":"區議會無實權過半都撚狗咁撚小強<br />\n立法會過半+唔剪布泛民主席 建制仲改議事規則俾大權主席<br />\n諗起都好玩"},{"pid":"0bd81bcfe17171511e97a04a40cb56c52abe8884","tid":1903043,"uid":157762,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:07:43.000Z","msg":"不如你睇下泛民投票記錄先"},{"pid":"64d2de26eb20b8bf080628e321bc570b7235e200","tid":1903043,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天琦講過：條條大佬通羅馬，放棄教條主義，邊個方法得就用邊個</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我希望全部手足都明白呢個道理"},{"pid":"42e33008d29e1eb534682162f43fb69639cfc723","tid":1903043,"uid":143526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:13:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7678b41630c1c033012b74268cfc373e86da93e1","tid":1903043,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17c5d9060682fe22fd5be2e0636be5c4690d88c","tid":1903043,"uid":31952,"like":0,